{
  "chapter": 224,
  "chapter_summary": "寇仲和徐子陵换上禁卫武服，混入尚秀芳的车队，企图借其掩护潜入皇城。在曼清院，寇仲假冒王世充派来的禁卫，成功说服随从头子白声允许他们随行。车队出发后，李世民偕庞玉、长孙无忌、尉迟敬德追来，原来他约了尚秀芳同行入宫。李世民与尚秀芳在途中谈及寇仲和徐子陵，称赞二人是天才横溢的绝代高手、智勇兼备，语气中透出对这两个劲敌的重视与无奈。车队顺利通过承福门进入宫城，寇仲二人趁暴雨倾盆之际溜至乾阳殿旁的钟楼。徐子陵利用长索和井中月，施展绝技将寇仲送上三十丈外的殿顶，两人吊在殿檐观察宴会厅内形势。王世充在殿内设午宴为尚秀芳饯行，李世民亦在座。寇仲和徐子陵商定分工：徐子陵负责擒拿王玄应，寇仲负责牵制李世民和尉迟敬德等人，趁尚秀芳开金口演唱之时动手。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秀芳小姐的车驾起行了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "把门者",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位官爷，秀芳小姐仍在梳洗，不过马车已准备好了，随时可以起行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我引路！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bai_sheng",
      "text": "玄应太子特别派我们来保护秀芳小姐，白兄该知近日东都事故频生吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白声",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "两位军爷脸生得很。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bai_sheng",
      "text": "我们这些日子来都跟玄感公子到了偃师办事，所以少有见面。不过上趟秀芳小姐到尚书府，我不是见过白兄吗？只不过我守在府内而已，还记得秀芳小姐第一首便是甚么'少年公子负恩生'，嘿！我只记得这一句，其他的都忘了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白声",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我也闻得东都不大太平，玄应太子果是有心。不过小姐素不喜欢张扬，两位军爷这么伴在两旁，只怕小姐不悦。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bai_sheng",
      "text": "这个容易，待会我们脱下军服，远远跟在队后便可以了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "现在只要能过得皇城入口那一关，我们便是过了海的神仙啦！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "秀芳小姐好！世民来迟了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "秦王一向准时，为何今天竟迟到了，秀芳并无任何见怪之意，只是心生好奇吧！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "秀芳小姐可还记得寇仲和徐子陵吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "提到寇仲！秀芳曾与他有两次同席之缘，印象颇深，总觉得他气质有异于其他人。至于徐子陵呢！只在听留阁惊鸿一瞥的隔远见过，仍未有机会认识。秦王的迟到难道是为了他们吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "秀芳小姐可知世民和他们本是好友，但现在却成了生死相拚的仇敌？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "秦王这些时日来，是否为了此事弄得心身皆忙呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "我刚才正为他们奔波，原来只是一场误会。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "寇仲不是为王公效力的吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "那是以前的事了。秀芳小姐不要让人世间的尔虞我诈沾污了双耳。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "他两人虽是武功高强，英雄了得，但若要与秦王作对，是否太不自量力呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "这两人已不可用武功高强来形容他们那么简单，他们可能是有史以来最天才横溢的绝代高手，更难得的是智勇兼备。所以直至今天，仍没有人能奈何得了他们。连想置他们于死地的李密最后都栽在他们手下，即此便可想见其馀。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "speaker_name": "尚秀芳",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "他们为今是否仍在东都？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_fang",
      "text": "这个非常难说，当他两人隐在暗里图谋时，谁都感到难以提防和测度！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你不是有方法可渡过这样的远距离吗？在这里是否可重施故技呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然可以，现在还更轻易，因为我们多了条原来用来攀城墙用的长索子。来吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今次要看你的能耐！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "若这方法到不了乾阳殿顶，那时便用来逃命好了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你至少该告诉我应怎样配合吧？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "非常简单，我把你送往空中，你再运气滑行，然后由小弟掷出井中月，你便学晃公错踏着飞钹般凭刀势投往目的地，记着至紧要运功把刀吸住，若\"叮\"的一声插在殿顶处，我们便要一起宣告完蛋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "真有你的！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "起！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "李小子这么公然出席王世充在宫殿内举行的盛会，是否等若间接承认王世充的帝位呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "亏你还有时间想这种事，李小子肯参加这午宴，当然有他的理由哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_shi_chong",
      "speaker_name": "王世充",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "秀芳大家今晚便要坐船离开，让我们都来敬她一杯，祝她一路顺风。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我诈作行刺王世充，你则负责去擒拿小玄应，如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "王世充由我负责，你去对付李小子，好把尉迟敬德那三个家伙牵制住。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "那谁去擒人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然是小弟，王玄应见到老爷遇袭，必会抢过来救驾，那就是他遭擒的一刻。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你小心点荣凤祥，只要他比荣姣姣更厉害一些，便够你头痛的。嘿！你说我会否一时错手把李小子宰掉呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们的目标是要救虚先生，你若贪功求胜，反被敌人擒下，我们便要全盘皆输，那时要换的便不是虚先生而是你这蠢家伙，明白了吗？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "在你面前，为何我总像是愚蠢的一个？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "何时动手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你说呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然是当敌人的警觉性降至最低的时刻！告诉我，那该在甚么时候动手？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这叫英雄所见略同，我们的秀芳大家开金口之时，就是我们出手的一刻哩。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 224,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 336
    }
  ],
